title: LAME - Locals Only - 6-23-13
description:
LAME
Locals Only - 107.3 The Point
Elizabethtown, KY
Broadcast Debut - 6-23-13

Recorded by: Axe for 107.3

live studio recording > adobe audition > MP3

Locals Only is a locally-produced radio show designed to give local musicians and bands valuable experience in a radio-studio setting as well as the exposure of local airplay.  Bands have the option of bringing their own studio recordings or recording an acoustic set live in the radio station, and sit for interview segments to introduce the band and music.

LAME chose to record live in-studio, and we hope you find the results as excellent as we did.  This performance is absolutely live, no dubs, no correction, exactly as heard in the studio on the night.  

Tracks: 

1. Interview 1
2. She Lies
3. Interview 2
4. Lou-Evil
5. Interview 3
6. Hospice

Enjoy!
